Subject: [PATCH 5/5] Emphasize one brain across channels: name web form,
 email, chat, phone explicitly + one consistent qualification record

---
 index.html | 4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/index.html b/index.html
index dbbf050..bd02bef 100644
--- a/index.html
+++ b/index.html
@@ -3539,8 +3539,8 @@
     <section class="page-section">
         <div class="statement">
             <h2>One brain.<br>Every channel you run.</h2>
-            <p class="lx-desk">Most tools cover one channel, and none of them share a brain. LUPO runs whichever channels your inbound comes through, one brain with shared context, so a buyer never starts over.</p>
-            <p class="lx-mob">Most tools cover one channel and don't share a brain. LUPO runs every channel on one brain, so a buyer never starts over.</p>
+            <p class="lx-desk">Most tools cover one channel, and none of them share a brain. LUPO runs one qualification brain across web form, email, chat, and phone, so buyers never start over and your team sees one consistent qualification record.</p>
+            <p class="lx-mob">Most tools cover one channel and don't share a brain. LUPO runs one brain across web form, email, chat, and phone, so buyers never start over.</p>
         </div>
     </section>
 
